昨晚 10 点多，记者联系到紫金陈，他表示正在去医院的路上，现在站不住，只能紧急去医院买止痛药，先扛一下。 晚 11 点，紫金陈告诉小时新闻记者，已经买好止痛药回家。 小时新闻记者昨晚试图联系医院，电话无人接听。作家紫金陈深夜维权：花4500“小分子祛炎针”治疗，越治越严重"},"attached_info":"Cj8Iicrmo6/O6M8uEAMaCDY0OTg2ODgwIKuVzIUGMAM4vQFAC3IJNDYyMTgzNjAweACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"122 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-1328b206b1d0ed2f841c176a8e64b29b_b.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"12_1622417212.665419","card_id":"Q_364828906","target":{"id":364828906,"title":"女孩子哪个瞬间会让你觉得很有教养?","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/364828906","type":"question","created":1578218680,"answer_count":360,"follower_count":4344,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[300,3803,14862],"comment_count":5,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"Cj8Iicrmo6/O6M8uEAMaCDQzMzUxMjE2ILjpxvAFMAU4+CFADHIJMzY0ODI4OTA2eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"112 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-82420ecc4944333565ea1ece32bc2867_b.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"13_1622417212.6657503","card_id":"Q_433945197","target":{"id":433945197,"title":"按照斗破苍穹的正常设定，假设你魂穿古河，如何迎娶云韵并保护云岚宗？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/433945197","type":"question","created":1607433353,"answer_count":28,"follower_count":61,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[172551,208380,208381],"comment_count":3,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"穿越的时间就是斗破苍穹第一章开始的时间，一开始你肯定搞不清楚状况，所以无法及时阻拦纳兰嫣然去退婚，有没有人发挥一下想象？ 动漫里的古河是真的帅，有点像凤舞九天的陆小凤，按现代人的道德观来看三观也很正，属于斗破苍穹那个世界里少有的老好人，对女神云韵一心一意而且也不趁人之危，性格方面特别像网上说的老实人，没有和云韵成为一对真的很可惜"},"attached_info":"Cj4Iicrmo6/O6M8uEAMaCDU4NzExMTQ1IIn5vf4FMAM4PUANcgk0MzM5NDUxOTd4AKoBCW